entries.quest_location_d: Multiple points through the Naboo System
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a patrol waypoint you will receive a new one to your next location. Follow each of the patrol waypoints until you reach the end of your patrol.  This is the first of four special assignments given to you by Captain Dinge of the RSF. When you complete this mission, return to Captain Dinge in the Theed Palace for your next assignment.  After you complete these four special assignments, Captain Dinge will train you in a new Pilot skill.

entries.title_d: Run a patrol through the Naboo System. When you complete this mission, return to Captain Dinge in the Theed Palace for your next assignment.
